responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "2C9ACBA149749F7407329187362DC192", "I cannot explain. Just know, I am not always myself. But you are not here to learn of my sundering. You were sent to recover my cursed curios before those who sundered me notice my existence here. Demons are merciless and vengeful till the end of time. ")
